{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Retro Punch Comp\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Soft Knee RMS type compressor. Comntrols...\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Comp Drive: Input gain to drive the compressor\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Speed: Controls both attack and release speed\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Intensity: This is almost a ratio control with invert setting for special effect\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Dry/Wet: Mix some uncompressed signal in for parellel compression\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Out gain: Controls output level, followed by soft clipper,then out drive\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Out Drive: Extra boost after clipper, using third harmonic waveshaper\sa180\par}
}

