{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Dirt EQ\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Is it a EQ? Is it distortion? NO! It's Dirt EQ! To use as EQ keep drive controls near or left of center. more EQ = more harmonics. To use as distortion, boost drive gain + IC1 + IC2 drive, try the filters first.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 SVF filter code from Andy Simper of cytomics\par}
}

